snippet.title: Another Space Opera Episode 1: The Wake of The Giant - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the announcement trailer for Another Space Opera - Episode 1: The Wake Of The Giant to see brutal gameplay set in a sci-fi world from this upcoming action platformer game. Another Space Opera - Episode 1: The Wake Of The Giant is coming to PC, PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X/S, and Nintendo Switch in 2023.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
